description:
Here you can train radio messages for the hessian Feuerwehr-Leistungsübung!
With our app you can train radio messages and commands for the hessian Feuerwehr Leistungsübung (HFLÜ). We use it for our local training-group and it is regularly updated if things change.

We are happy to receive feedback or feature requests :)

#HFLÜ #Hessische #Feuerwehr #Leistungsübung #Funk-Trainer
